author: Journal sports staff
title: Patriots-Cowboys pregame quiz: Test your knowledge
text: Posted Oct. 8, 2015 at 9:30 AM By Journal sports staff Posted Oct. 8, 2015 at 9:30 AM They are two of the NFL's signature franchises, but the Cowboys and the Patriots don't have a long history of memorable games. Maybe that will change on Sunday , when they meet for the 12th time. Get ready for the game by taking our weekly quiz. Come back for next week's Patriots pregame quiz. Find more on the Pats at providencejournal.com/patriots Follow Providence Journal sports writer Mark Daniels on Twitter @MarkDanielsPJ By Journal sports staff
